## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1a573-102">這個例外狀況衍生自<xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>，代表在應用程式應能處理端點的穩定的 Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) 用戶端與服務之間進行通訊時可能會擲回可修復錯誤的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a573-102">This exception derives from <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> that represents a class of recoverable errors that may be thrown during communication between endpoints and which robust Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) client and service applications are expected to handle.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1a573-103">若要避免由比較泛型的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 處理常式來攔截比較特定的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ActionNotSupportedException>，請在處理 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 之前攔截此例外狀況 (Exception)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a573-103">To prevent the more generic <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> handler from catching the more specific <xref:System.ServiceModel.ActionNotSupportedException>, catch this exception prior to handling <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
